            "id": 5915818,
            "title": "軍工股晟田漲停⊕只是前菜、買價值、買修正、買被錯殺好股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今日看盤重點</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今日的恐慌下殺再創近期新低</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>一點都不意外！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要原因除了受到川普恐嚇式關稅威脅的衝擊影響外</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>再者，在量縮利空淬煉底部的過程中</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>本來就是會持續不斷地反覆震盪探底</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>這一點之前也都跟大家提醒過</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>直到許多人都「哀莫大於心死」之時</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>就是台股準備展開報復性反彈的時候</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而這個時機點</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>預計在清明節前後將可望浮現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>這是大家可留意與掌握的機會</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>當報復性反彈來臨時</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>現階段重點是</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>那些是對的股票、策略拉回找買點？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>那些不對的股票、策略反彈找賣點？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>很重要！你一定要知道</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>千萬別傻傻的分不清楚</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>譬如聯鈞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3450:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3450\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3450-TW</a>)、亞光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3019:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3019\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3019-TW</a>)、和椿 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6215:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6215\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6215-TW</a>)… 等高基期漲高股</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著股價大漲上來、估值已偏高之下</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>之前大師兄也都有提醒大家</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高檔不追見好就收、尾巴留給別人去拚</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>相信大家都有目共賭！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>再來像新唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4919-TW</a>)、廣運 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6125:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6125\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6125-TW</a>)、先進光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3362:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3362\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3362-TW</a>)、鈺創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5351-TW</a>)… 等</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>我常說：「醜媳婦總是要見公婆」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>對於哪些產業面仍存有疑慮、公司營運及獲利不如預期的趨勢轉弱股</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>基於風險考量</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>策略上就是要懂得反彈找賣點</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過，礙於篇幅有限</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>我不可能一檔一檔列舉出來</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>如果您有持股上的問題</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不曉得如何來處理或調整</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大家也不必客氣</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>歡迎加 Line 私訊大師兄</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記得留下你的姓名和連絡電話</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>或直接來電洽詢 (每人限 5 檔)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大師兄情義相挺來助你一臂之力</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\